data.description: Updated ranch in a quiet family friendly neighborhood. Including lake and beach access to Scott lake. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths with a spacious kitchen. Granite countertops, vaulted ceiling in main room and freshly painted. Finished basement with utility room for laundry and a large amount of storage. Fenced in backyard with fire pit. Detached 2 car garage with gas heater and workshop area. The garage has its own electrical panel and attic access  for ample storage.
